### Import Multiple Students from Excel (Admin/Staff only)
### Excel file should have columns: LastName, FirstName, MiddleName (optional)
POST {{BackendTechnicalAssetsManagement_HostAddress}}/api/v1/users/students/import
Authorization: Bearer {your-jwt-token}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="students.xlsx"
Content-Type: application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet

< ./path/to/students.xlsx
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

